"""
Mahakaal Options Sniper v5.0
=============================
GCP VM | Kotak Neo | Zero Brokerage
Scalp Trends. Sell Chop. Stay Silent Otherwise.

Architecture:
  Day Classification  → 15-min ADX + ER + OR + Gap + VWAP (locked 10:30 AM)
  Scalp Mode          → 5 lots | Supertrend + Pivot + OR break + VWAP + L2
  Sell Mode           → 2 lots | Spreads only | After 10:30 AM | DTE 3-5
  No Trade            → Mixed signals → complete silence

Schedule:
  8:30 AM  → Auto TOTP login
  9:00 AM  → Pre-market brief
  9:15 AM  → OR tracking
  9:30 AM  → OR lock + asset check
  9:45 AM  → Tentative classification
  10:30 AM → Mode LOCKED
  Every 5m → Signals + monitor
  2:30 PM  → Hard exit sells
  2:55 PM  → Pre-close
  3:00 PM  → Hard exit all
  3:30 PM  → EOD summary
"""

